{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"31b628c3-9895-44c0-a28f-8849b81b1f1e","content":"In MSTest v3, `.testsettings` files are **no longer supported**. You need to migrate to a `.runsettings` file. Here's how to replace each setting from your `local.testsettings`:\n\n| `.testsettings` setting | `.runsettings` equivalent |\n|---|---|\n| `TestTimeout` (30s) | `<MSTest><TestTimeout>` |\n| Code coverage collector | `<DataCollectors>` section |\n| `AssemblyResolution` / deployment | No longer needed (MSTest v3 runs in-place) |\n\nLet me create the replacement `.runsettings` file:","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"tooluse_Mw88m3hcRo8SMqnJO5GgU5","name":"create","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-e1dd44ea85d148e2ae66d176b2d42af9/local.runsettings","file_text":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<RunSettings>\n  <MSTest>\n    <TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout>\n  </MSTest>\n  <DataCollectionRunSettings>\n    <DataCollectors>\n      <DataCollector friendlyName=\"Code Coverage\"\n        uri=\"datacollector://Microsoft/CodeCoverage/2.0\"\n        assemblyQualifiedName=\"Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector.VanguardCollector, Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b03f5f7f11d50a3a\">\n      </DataCollector>\n    </DataCollectors>\n  </DataCollectionRunSettings>\n</RunSettings>\n"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"create a new file at /tmp/sv-e1dd44ea85d148e2ae66d176b2d42af9/local.runsettings."}],"interactionId":"2247ad31-b022-47d3-b4db-fff2cbc96430","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user has a `.testsettings` file with:\n1. Assembly resolution/deployment settings\n2. A test timeout of 30000ms (30 seconds)\n3. A code coverage data collector\n\nIn MSTest v3, `.testsettings` files are no longer supported. The user needs to migrate to a `.runsettings` file. Let me explain how to migrate each setting.\n\nFor MSTest v3:\n- `.testsettings` is deprecated/ignored\n- Configuration should be moved to a `.runsettings` file\n- Test timeout can be set via `[Timeout]` attribute, or in `.runsettings` under `<MSTest><TestTimeout>`\n\n\n- Code coverage and deployment settings are configured in `.runsettings` under `<DataCollectors>` and handled differently in MSTest v3\n\nNow I'll create a `.runsettings` file that replaces the `.testsettings` configuration.","outputTokens":665,"requestId":"5829:39B639:1594290:16F2914:6A045FD2"},"id":"a6ac7daf-71c1-4212-b90e-8271caab402f","timestamp":"2026-05-13T11:26:21.785Z","parentId":"b0d02fa3-eaa0-40d1-9a0b-410f54ee8c1d"}
